        },
        "text_zx9zic": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Everything you need to start making custom apparel at home.</p>",
            "text_custom": true,
            "text_font": "inter_n6",
            "text_size": 18,
            "text_size_mobile": 16,
            "text_height": 130,
            "text_mt": 20,
            "text_mt_mobile": 20,
            "text_align": "left",
            "text_align_mobile": "center",
            "text_color": "#373434"
          }
        },
        "item_Kjcy7E": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What are Ninja Transfers?",
            "answer": "<p>Ninja's DTF transfers are custom heat-press designs printed on a special film. You apply them to clothing using a heat press or iron, and the design bonds to the fabric for a durable, professional look.</p>",
            "linkText": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "item_CGkw7y": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do I need special equipment to apply them?",
            "answer": "<p>No. Many customers successfully apply transfers using a regular household iron. A Cricut EasyPress or heat press makes it easier and more consistent, but an iron works great for beginners and at-home projects.</p>",
            "linkText": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "item_68FNKy": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What types of clothing or fabrics can I use them on?",
            "answer": "<p>DTF transfers work on almost any fabric, including cotton, polyester, blends, and light or dark colors. They’re great for shirts, hoodies, hats, totes, and more.</p>",
            "linkText": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "item_T7MHLm": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are these safe for kids’ clothing and everyday wear?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. DTF transfers are designed for everyday use and are commonly used on kids’ apparel and family wear.</p>",
            "linkText": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "item_wLEMMK": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are DTF transfers easy to use if I’ve never done this before?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. They’re beginner-friendly and designed to be simple to apply, even if it’s your first time making custom apparel.</p>",
            "linkText": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "item_VWCEbW": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What if I make a mistake when pressing?",
            "answer": "<p>If an area doesn’t fully adhere, you can usually re-press it with more heat or pressure. Detailed instructions are included to help you get the best result.</p>",
            "linkText": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "item_k4qR9G": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I wash and wear it like normal?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Once applied, your apparel can be worn and washed like usual. Just follow the garments basic care instructions.</p>",
            "linkText": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
      },
